snippet.title: Rabbi Simon Jacobson at Meaningful Life Center
snippet.description: The Meaningful Life Center, founded by Simon Jacobson, is dedicated to helping everyone to lead a more meaningful life. Unlock yourself. Discover the tools to find YOUR mission in life.
